            Supportive care for Parkinson's symptoms using acupuncture to improve quality of life.
          </p>
        </article>
        <article class="service-card">
          <div class="icon" aria-hidden="true">🌺</div>
          <h3>Women's Menopause</h3>
          <p>
            Natural menopause symptom management through traditional Korean medicine approaches.
          </p>
        </article>
        <article class="service-card">
          <div class="icon" aria-hidden="true">🤱</div>
          <h3>Infertility</h3>
