            Fertility support using acupuncture and herbal medicine to enhance reproductive health.
          </p>
        </article>
        <article class="service-card">
          <div class="icon" aria-hidden="true">👨</div>
          <h3>Prostatic Disorder</h3>
          <p>
            Treatment for prostate-related conditions using traditional medicine techniques.
          </p>
        </article>
        <article class="service-card">
          <div class="icon" aria-hidden="true">🥗</div>
          <h3>Digestive System Disorder</h3>
          <p>
            Comprehensive treatment for digestive issues including stomach, intestinal, and bowel disorders.
          </p>
        </article>
        <article class="service-card">
          <div class="icon" aria-hidden="true">🔬</div>
          <h3>Crohn's Disease</h3>
          <p>
            Supportive care for inflammatory bowel disease using acupuncture and herbal treatments.
          </p>
        </article>
        <article class="service-card">
          <div class="icon" aria-hidden="true">🧬</div>
          <h3>Stroke</h3>
          <p>
            Post-stroke rehabilitation support through acupuncture to aid recovery and improve function.
          </p>
        </article>
        <article class="service-card">
          <div class="icon" aria-hidden="true">😶</div>
          <h3>Bell's Palsy</h3>
          <p>
            Facial nerve paralysis treatment using specialized acupuncture techniques for recovery.
          </p>
        </article>
        <article class="service-card">
          <div class="icon" aria-hidden="true">🍯</div>
          <h3>Diabetes</h3>
          <p>
            Complementary treatment for diabetes management through traditional Korean medicine.
          </p>
        </article>
        <article class="service-card">
          <div class="icon" aria-hidden="true">❤️</div>
          <h3>High Blood Pressure</h3>
          <p>
            Natural approaches to blood pressure management using acupuncture and lifestyle guidance.
          </p>
        </article>
        <article class="service-card">
          <div class="icon" aria-hidden="true">🏃</div>
          <h3>Weight Management</h3>
          <p>
            Holistic weight management program combining acupuncture, herbal medicine, and dietary guidance.
          </p>
        </article>
        <article class="service-card">
          <div class="icon" aria-hidden="true">🎭</div>
          <h3>Skin Issues</h3>
          <p>
            Treatment for various skin conditions including eczema, psoriasis, and other dermatological issues.
          </p>
        </article>
        <article class="service-card">
          <div class="icon" aria-hidden="true">😴</div>
          <h3>Insomnia</h3>
          <p>
            Natural sleep disorder treatment using acupuncture and herbal medicine for better rest.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section about" id="about" aria-labelledby="about-heading">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 id="about-heading">
        About Riverside's Leading Acupuncture Clinic - Woori Acupuncture
      </h2>
      <div class="about-content">
        <div class="about-text">
          <p>
            <strong>Woori Acupuncture</strong> is Riverside's premier acupuncture clinic, combining authentic traditional Korean
            medicine with modern therapeutic techniques to provide the highest quality
            care for patients throughout Riverside, California and surrounding areas. With years of experience
            and specialized training, we offer personalized treatments tailored to
            each patient's individual condition for fundamental health recovery and
            long-term wellness.
          </p>
          <p>
            Our holistic approach focuses on treating the root cause of health
            issues rather than just managing symptoms, promoting natural healing
            processes and sustainable wellness. Located in the heart of Riverside, CA,
            we serve patients from throughout the Inland Empire including Corona, Moreno Valley,
            and surrounding communities. We are committed to helping Riverside residents
            achieve optimal health through time-tested traditional Korean medicine methods.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-image">
          <img
            src="/woori-acu-clinic-1.jpg"
            alt="Professional acupuncture treatment room at Woori Acupuncture clinic in Riverside, California"
            loading="lazy"
            width="400"
            height="300"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section
    class="section contact-info"
    id="contact"
    aria-labelledby="contact-heading"
  >
    <div class="container">
      <h2 id="contact-heading" style="color: white;">
        Contact Riverside's Top Acupuncture Clinic - Schedule Your Appointment Today
      </h2>
      <div class="contact-grid">
        <article class="contact-item">
          <div class="icon" aria-hidden="true">📍</div>
          <h3>Riverside Clinic Location</h3>
          <address>
            3579 Arlington Ave Suite 900<br />
            Riverside, California 92506<br />
            <small>Serving Riverside, Corona, Moreno Valley & Inland Empire</small>
          </address>
        </article>
        <article class="contact-item">
          <div class="icon" aria-hidden="true">📞</div>
          <h3>Phone Numbers</h3>
          <p>
            Office: <a href="tel:+19517771011" rel="nofollow">(951) 777-1011</a
            ><br />
            Mobile: <a href="tel:+17142610605" rel="nofollow">(714) 261-0605</a
            ><br />
          </p>
        </article>
        <article class="contact-item">
          <div class="icon" aria-hidden="true">🕐</div>
          <h3>Business Hours</h3>
          <div>
            Monday-Friday: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM<br />
            Saturday: 9:00 AM - 3:00 PM<br />
            Sunday: Closed
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="map-section">
        <Map lat={33.9466568} lng={-117.3915209} zoom={15} height="500px" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <div class="container">
      <p>&copy; 2025 Woori Acupuncture. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>

